(110, 1, '2019-05-10 17:15:31', '2019-05-10 17:15:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Antara Biswas also known as Mona Lisa&nbsp; is an Indian actress mostly known for Bhojpuri motion picture industry. She has done over 125 Bhojpuri films, and has also act in Hindi, Bengali, Oriya, Tamil, Kannada and Telugu films. She was a participants of Indian show Bigg Boss 10 in 2016. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":114,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Mona-lisa-Antara-Biswas-very-Hot-Photos.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Mona-lisa-Antara-Biswas-very-Hot-Photos.jpg\" alt=\"Mona lisa Antara Biswas very Hot Photos\" class=\"wp-image-114\"/></a><figcaption>Mona lisa Antara Biswas very Hot Photos</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She was born and brought up in Kolkata, West Bengal into a Hindu-Bengali family. She began her profession with first Bhojpuri film “Bole Shankar” which was released in 2008. Monalisa is the stand out performing artist who worked with practically every Bhojpuri whizzes like Pawan Singh, Dinesh Lal Yadav and others. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":115,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/monalisa-hot.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/monalisa-hot.jpg\" alt=\"Antara Biswas Photo\" class=\"wp-image-115\"/></a><figcaption>Antara Biswas Photo<br></figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Antara Biswas can be credited for the rise of the Bhojpuri industry in recent years. Her strong on-screen presence is highly appreciated by the audience and has won millions of hearts. In 2010, Th