(140, 1, '2019-05-17 20:10:45', '2019-05-17 20:10:45', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Niharika Konidela is a promising Indian Film and Television Actress &amp; Producer. She was born 18 December 1993 in Hyderabad, Telangana, India. She has completed Graduation from St. Mary’s College, Hyderabad. Niharika Konidela mainly works in Telugu and Tamil Films.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":163,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Niharika-Konidela-3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Niharika-Konidela-3.jpg\" alt=\"Niharika Konidela\" class=\"wp-image-163\"/></a><figcaption>Niharika Konidela</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She started her career with the Telugu dance reality show Dhee Juniors 1 and Dhee Juniors 2 aired on ETV Telugu. After that she acted and also produced the Telugu Web-Series Muddapappu Avakai. She was made her on-screen debut with film ‘Oka Manasu’ (2016). She also worked in Telugu films, Nanna Koochi (2017) and Upcoming film Happy Wedding (2018). Niharika Konidela is looking so pretty, talented and most popular for her mind bowling acting. She acted in a Tamil movie Oru Nalla Naal Paathu Solren in 2018</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Her Father is Nagendra Babu who is an Actor &amp; Producer and Her Mother is Padmaja Konidela. She has one brother named, Varun Tej who is an actor. Niharika Konidela is Unmarried and She is in a relationship with Actor Sai Dharam Tej. She confessed that she owes a lot to her father, Naga Babu, who has been a pillar of strength all her life. There are rumors that Niharika and her father Nagababu are looking for good story and if they like any they are ready to produce for the movie.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Wiki an