(171, 1, '2019-05-25 10:00:39', '2019-05-25 10:00:39', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sri Reddy is a Telugu Actress and Video Jockey. She mainly works in Telugu Flim Industry &amp; Telugu TV Shows. She started her career as a Newsreader and hosted few entertainment events. She also done in several print shoots and TV Commercial ads.&nbsp; After that she started her movies career. She made her debut in Telugu Film ‘Neenu Naana Abaddam’ in 2011.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":187,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Sri-Reddy-selfie.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Sri-Reddy-selfie.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-187\"/></a><figcaption>Sri Reddy</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sri Reddy is born on 12 June 1992. She born and brought up in Vijayawada, India. Currently, she becomes a news sensation due to her Protest. Actually, she is a victim of casting couch so Sri Reddy did a protest. She protest on the street against ‘casting couch’.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the Telugu film industry has heated up with actor Sri Reddy threatening to name and shame the men who indulge in the practice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Controversy</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She is trending is news because she is Protesting against Casting Couch in Telugu Film Industry. Sri Reddy staged a protest against sexual harassment in Tollywood by stripping in front of the office of Movie Artistes Association. Currently, this is trending news about her. A new turn comes in this case Sri Reddy accuses Suresh Babu’s Son Abhiram Daggubati of ‘sexploitation’. She leaked some pictures by her own.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -