(173, 1, '2019-05-25 10:11:20', '2019-05-25 10:11:20', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sargun Mehta also known as Sargun Mehta Dubey, is an Indian actress, model, and television host. The recipient of a Filmfare Award, she works predominantly in Punjabi language films. She was born on 6 September 1988 in Chandigarh, India. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":195,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta.png\" alt=\"Sargun Mehta\" class=\"wp-image-195\"/></a><figcaption>Sargun Mehta</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sargun Mehta Father Name is Harish Mehta and her mother name is Aradhana Mehta. She has a younger brother. As a child, along with her brother, Mehta auditioned for the dance reality show Boogie Woogie; they were both rejected. Mehta did her schooling at the Sacred Heart Convent school and Carmel Convent School in Chandigarh. She did her graduation in Bachelor of commerce from the Kirori Mal College, Delhi University. She then began studying for a Master\'s degree in Business Management, but left to pursue her acting career. Sargun Mehta Married to Ravi Dubey in 7 December 2013.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mehta began acting in theatre productions in her college, later she works in Hindi Television Serials. She was made her screen debut in TV Series 12-/24 Karol Bagh (2009) as Neetu Sehi Dagar. After that she works on Colors TV\'s drama series Phulwa which was a significant turning point in her career, earning her critical appreciation. She has been appeared in many Popular TV serials including “Nach Baliye 5, Balika Vadhu, Nach Baliye 6, Comedy Nights with Kapil, Bigg Boss 8, Nach Baliye 7, Bigg Boss 9 and The Kapil Sharma Show”. Sargun Mehta Also Appeared in few Punjabi Movies Including “Angrej, Love Punjab”. Sargun Mehta upcoming Punjabi Movies Jindua and Lahoriye” Both Films will release in 2017. Sargun Mehta has been received Indian Television Academy Awards for Balika Vadu serial and PTV Punjabi Film Awards for The Punjabi Film Angrej.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Sargun Mehta Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[\"198\",\"199\",\"200\",\"201\",\"202\",\"203\"],\"linkTo\":\"media\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-cute.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-cute.jpg\" alt=\"Sargun Mehta Photoshoot\" data-id=\"198\" class=\"wp-image-198\"/></a><figcaption>Sargun Mehta Photoshoot</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-hd-photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-hd-photo.jpg\" alt=\"Sargun Mehta after Gym\" data-id=\"199\" class=\"wp-image-199\"/></a><figcaption>Sargun Mehta after Gym</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-hd-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-hd-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Sargun Mehta Wallpaper\" data-id=\"200\" class=\"wp-image-200\"/></a><figcaption>Sargun Mehta Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-hot.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-hot.jpg\" alt=\"Sargun Mehta Hot\" data-id=\"201\" class=\"wp-image-201\"/></a><figcaption>Sargun Mehta Hot</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-photo.jpg\" alt=\"Sargun Mehta Selfie\" data-id=\"202\" class=\"wp-image-202\"/></a><figcaption>Sargun Mehta Selfie</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sargun-mehta-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Sargun Mehta Cute Photo\" data-id=\"203\" class=\"wp-image-203\"/></a><figcaption>Sargun Mehta Cute Photo</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->', 'Sargun Mehta Wiki | Salary | Biography | Height | Photo', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sargun-mehta', '', '', '2019-05-25 19:17:13', '2019-05-25 19:17:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=173', 0, 'post', '', 0),
