(215, 1, '2019-05-25 17:16:55', '2019-05-25 17:16:55', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tiger Shroff is an Indian film actor and youngest superstar of Bollywood. He was born in 2 March 1990. He is the son of famous actor Jackie Shroff and producer Ayesha Dutt. His sister Krishna Shroff is three years younger than him. His real name is <strong>Jai Hemant Shroff</strong>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":229,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff\" class=\"wp-image-229\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff<br></figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Early life and education </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tiger completed his studies from the American School of Bombay. After that, he went to Amity University, Noida to pursue his further education but couldn’t complete it. At the age of 4, he is in the practice of martial arts. Tiger Shroff was very fond of football and wanted to be a football player at that time, but his fate would eventually make him an actor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":230,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-and-family.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-and-family.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff with family\" class=\"wp-image-230\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff with family\n\n</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tiger Shroff is a 5th degree black belt in Taekwondo and is given by the Kukkiwon-World Taekwondo Headquarters. It is believed that he is a young icon who inspires young people to learn martial arts for self defense.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Tiger Shroff Filmography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tiger Shroff has been working in many commercially successful films such as Horopathy, Baghi, A Flying Jatt, Munna Michael Tiger Shroff in his forthcoming film Baji 2, Rambo and Dumbura. He has also done three music videos on \"Zindagi Aa Ru Hoon Main\", Chil Wah Jat Hain and befikra.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":231,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff-and-Disha-Patani.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff-and-Disha-Patani.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff and Disha Patani\" class=\"wp-image-231\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff and Disha Patani</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Facts about Tiger Shroff</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Tiger Shroff is alleged to be dating the Baaghi 2 actress&nbsp;<strong>Disha Patani</strong>.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Shraddha Kapoor</strong>&nbsp;is the best friend and classmate of Tiger.&nbsp;</li><li>He is an ardent fan of WWE wrestling.&nbsp;</li><li>His all time favourite movie is Enter the Dragon.&nbsp;</li><li>Tiger Shroff helped&nbsp;<strong>Aamir Khan</strong>&nbsp;to build his physique for Dhoom 3.</li><li>Tiger Shroff is the brand Ambassador and co-owner of Bengaluru Tigers, which is owned by 8K Miles Media Group.</li><li>His major hobby is dancing.</li><li><strong>Akshay Kumar</strong>&nbsp;admire in an interview that, Tiger is a shy and introvert person and is very secretive in nature.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Tiger Shroff Salary and net worth</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tiger Shroff played lead role for Baaghi which earn ₹1.3 billion (US$18 million). Sequel of that movie is Baaghi 2 (2018), which earned over ₹2.6 billion (US$36 million) worldwide. Tiger Shroff Salary was ₹12 crores for his movie Baaghi 2. His net worth is $10 million. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Tiger Shroff Awards and Accolades</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Life Ok Award (Best Debutant)</li><li>Box Office Award (Biggest Box Office for Solo Male Lead)</li><li>Stardust Award (Superstar of Tomorrow)</li><li>Big Star Entertainment (Best Debut Male)</li><li>Lions Club Award (Best Debut), Star Guild (Most Promising Debut Male)</li><li>Screen Award (Most Promising Newcomer Male)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Tiger Shroff Photo</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[232,233,234,239,241,242],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"aligncenter\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-HD-photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-HD-photo.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff HD Photo\" data-id=\"232\" class=\"wp-image-232\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff HD Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-photo.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff Cute Photo\" data-id=\"233\" class=\"wp-image-233\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff Cute Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff Wallpaper\" data-id=\"234\" class=\"wp-image-234\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff-in-gym.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff-in-gym.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff in Gym\" data-id=\"239\" class=\"wp-image-239\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff in Gym</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff-in-baaghi-2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Tiger-Shroff-in-baaghi-2.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff in baaghi 2\" data-id=\"241\" class=\"wp-image-241\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff in baaghi 2</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-HD-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/tiger-shroff-HD-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Tiger Shroff HD wallpaper\" data-id=\"242\" class=\"wp-image-242\"/></a><figcaption>Tiger Shroff HD wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->', 'Tiger Shroff', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tiger-shroff', '', '', '2019-08-30 20:12:45', '2019-08-30 20:12:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=215', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(218, 1, '2019-05-25 17:20:33', '2019-05-25 17:20:33', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Varun Dhawan is an Indian film actor and youngest superstar of bollywood. He known as \"Bona Fide Bollywood Superstar\" for his acting skills. Varun Dhawan was born on 24 April 1987 in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. He is the son of film director and producer David Dhawan. His nickname is Pappu. He has an elder brother named Rohit Dhawan he is a well-known film director while his uncle, Anil Dhawan is an actor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":245,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan\" class=\"wp-image-245\"/></a><figcaption>Varun Dhawan</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Career</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He was an intelligent student and secured 82% his 10th board examination. Varun Dhawan Completed his studies in business management from the Nottingham Trent University. After that he worked as an assistant director to Karan Johar on the 2010 drama movie My Name Is Khan. He debuted his acting career with Alia Bhatt in Karan Johar\'s 2012 teen drama Student of the Year which is a box office successful film.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":246,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-childhood.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-childhood.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan Childhood Pic\" class=\"wp-image-246\"/></a><figcaption>Varun Dhawan Childhood Pic</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Varun Dhawan also acted opposite of Shraddha Kapoor in a sequel to the dance film ABCD: Any Body Can Dance, entitled ABCD 2, in which he portrays the real life character of Suresh Mukund, a dancer from Mumbai who wins the 2012 World Hip Hop Dance Championship. ABCD 2 earned ₹1.57 billion (US$23 million) worldwide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Varun Dhawan then played Rakesh \"Humpty Sharma\", a flirtatious Punjabi boy who engages in a romantic affair with an engaged woman, in Shashank Khaitan\'s romantic comedy Humpty Sharma Ki Dulhania. Co-starring Alia Bhatt and Siddharth Shukla, the film was described as a tribute to Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge (1995) by Johar, who served as producer. This film earned ₹1.11 billion (US$16 million) worldwide.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Filmography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Still now all movies of Varun Dhawan very successful in box office and there is no flop movie in his list. Please find the below list of all movies played by him.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>2012 Student of the Year</li><li>2014 Main Tera Hero</li><li>2014 Humpty Sharma Ki Dulhania</li><li>2015 Badlapur</li><li>2015 ABCD 2</li><li>2015 Dilwale</li><li>2016 Dishoom</li><li>2017 Badrinath Ki Dulhania</li><li>2017 Judwaa 2</li><li>2018 October</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Controversy</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There was a rumour that after an argument, actor Sohail Khan slapped Varun, but they both denied it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Awards<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Varun Dhawan has received by many awards &amp; Nominations for his acting performance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>He received a Filmfare nomination for Best Male Debut for Student of the Year.</li><li>In 2014, he appeared in Forbes India‘s Celebrity 100 list</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salary</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Varun Dhawan asked around Rs 25 crore per movie.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Varun Dhawan Photo</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[247,248,249,251,252],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"aligncenter\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-alia-bhatt.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-alia-bhatt.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan with Alia Bhatt\" data-id=\"247\" class=\"wp-image-247\"/></a><figcaption>Varun Dhawan with Alia Bhatt</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-hd-pic.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-hd-pic.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan HD Pic\" data-id=\"248\" class=\"wp-image-248\"/></a><figcaption>Varun Dhawan HD Pic</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan wallpaper\" data-id=\"249\" class=\"wp-image-249\"/></a><figcaption>Varun Dhawan wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-at-airport.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-at-airport.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan at Airport\" data-id=\"251\" class=\"wp-image-251\"/></a><figcaption>Varun Dhawan at Airport</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-hd-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/varun-dhawan-hd-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Varun Dhawan HD Wallpaper\" data-id=\"252\" class=\"wp-image-252\"/></a><figcaption>Varun Dhawan HD Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->', 'Varun Dhawan', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'varun-dhawan', '', '', '2019-05-25 20:09:54', '2019-05-25 20:09:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=218', 0, 'post', '', 0),
