(269, 1, '2019-05-27 20:19:16', '2019-05-27 20:19:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sara Ali Khan is the daughter of pronounced actor and actress Saif Ali Khan and Amrita Singh. She is an upcoming actress in bollywood film industry. Her grandfather, Mansoor Ali Khan Pataudi was a well-known Former Indian cricketer while her grandmother Sharmila Tagore is a great actress. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":279,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-photo.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan Photo\" class=\"wp-image-279\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan Photo</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Her parents got divorced in 2004 after 13 years of their marriage. After that her father got married to popular Bollywood actress Kareena Kapoor on 16 October 2012. Her Brother is Ibrahim Ali Khan and also she has a stepbrother Taimur Ali Khan.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sara Ali Khan was born and brought up in a Nawab’s family with the Islam ethnicity in the Mumbai. Her grandfather, Mansoor Ali Khan Pataudi was a well-known Former Indian cricketer while her grandmother Sharmila Tagore is a great actress.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":283,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-with-her-mom.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-with-her-mom.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan with her mom\" class=\"wp-image-283\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan with her mom Amrita Singh</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She had completed her education in 2016 from the famous Columbia University in New York. As follow the footstep of her parents Sara is also choose acting as a career, everyone waiting for her first movie. She appeared on the cover page of the Hello magazine along with her mother.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":284,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-with-saif.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-with-saif.png\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan with Saif Ali Khan\" class=\"wp-image-284\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan with Saif Ali Khan</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sara Ali Khan is currently unmarried and if rumors to be believed she is a relationship with Vivek Pahariya, who is the son of the famous politician- Sushil Kumar Shinde. Another rumors said she is now dating Harshvardhan Kapoor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Sara Ali Khan Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[285,286,287,288,289,290],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan3.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan3.png\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan in Kedarnath movie set\" data-id=\"285\" class=\"wp-image-285\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan in Kedarnath movie set</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-candid.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-candid.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan relaxing\" data-id=\"286\" class=\"wp-image-286\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan relaxing</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-hot.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-hot.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan Hot Photo\" data-id=\"287\" class=\"wp-image-287\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan Hot Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-Kartik-Aaryan.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-Kartik-Aaryan.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan with Kartik Aaryan\" data-id=\"288\" class=\"wp-image-288\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan with Kartik Aaryan</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-photoshoot.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-photoshoot.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan Photoshoot in beach side\" data-id=\"289\" class=\"wp-image-289\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan Photoshoot in beach side</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/sara-ali-khan-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Sara Ali Khan Wallpaper\" data-id=\"290\" class=\"wp-image-290\"/></a><figcaption>Sara Ali Khan Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->', 'Sara Ali Khan', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sara-ali-khan', '', '', '2019-06-06 18:33:34', '2019-06-06 18:33:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=269', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(272, 1, '2019-05-27 20:21:48', '2019-05-27 20:21:48', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rukmini Maitra is an Indian Model and Actress from Kolkata, who has worked as a model for various regional, national and international brands and magazines. After having established herself in the world of fashion, Rukmini made her silver screen debut in 2017.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":293,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/rukmini-maitra.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/rukmini-maitra.jpg\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra\" class=\"wp-image-293\"/></a><figcaption>Rukmini Maitra</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rukmini started her career as a model at the age of 13. She is brand ambassador of many pronounced brands and magazines such as Reliance, Lakmé, Vodafone, Sunsilk, Parachute, Titan etc. She has also worked for some famous fashion designers like Masaba Gupta, Anita Dongre, Suneet Varma, Dev r Nil, Anju Modi etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rukmini Maitra started her acting career with engali film titled Champ opposite Bengali Superstar Dev which was released in Eid 2017. The film was directed by Raj Chakraborty. The story of the film is based on boxing. Her latest movie is Kabir which is an Indian Bengali-language film, directed by Aniket Chattopadhyay and released on 13 April 2018.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Social Media</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/rukminimaitra/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/IamRukmini/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/RukminiMaitra</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rukmini_Maitra</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Rukmini Maitra Photo<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[294,295,296,297,298,299,301,302],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra1.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra1.png\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra Photo\" data-id=\"294\" class=\"wp-image-294\"/></a><figcaption>Rukmini Maitra Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra2.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra2.png\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra Poster\" data-id=\"295\" class=\"wp-image-295\"/></a><figcaption>Rukmini Maitra Poster</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra3.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra3.png\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra with Dev\" data-id=\"296\" class=\"wp-image-296\"/></a><figcaption>Rukmini Maitra with Dev</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra4.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra4.png\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra Picture\" data-id=\"297\" class=\"wp-image-297\"/></a><figcaption>Rukmini Maitra Picture</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra5.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Rukmini_Maitra5.png\" alt=\"Rukmini Maitra HD Photo\" da