(275, 1, '2019-05-27 20:24:23', '2019-05-27 20:24:23', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ananya Pandey is a star kid of Bollywood Industry. She was born on 29 March 1999 in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. She is the daughter of popular Bollywood actor Chunky Pandey and Bhavna Pandey.&nbsp; As per the information available, she completed her education from Dhirubhai Ambani International School in Mumbai. She went to the University of Southern California in Los Angeles for higher education.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":305,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Ananya-Panday2.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Ananya-Panday2.png\" alt=\"Ananya Pandey Photo\" class=\"wp-image-305\"/></a><figcaption>Ananya Pandey Photo</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Shah Rukh and Gauri Khan\'s daughter Suhana and Sanjay and Maheep Kapoor\'s daughter Shanaya is bestie of Ananya Panday. Now Ananya Pandey is totally ready her Bollywood debut. Before her debut, she\'s already is a social media sensation, courtesy her looks and her cuteness.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ananya Pandey and Tara Sutaria along with Tiger Shroff currently busy in shooting of their debut movie ‘Student of The Year 2’ (SOTY 2). Theshooting was started in the St. Teresa School, Dehradun. After that the cast have moved to Mussoorie. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Social Media <br></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/ananyapandayfp/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/ananyapaanday/</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Ananya Pandey Pho