(314, 1, '2019-06-06 19:07:39', '2019-06-06 19:07:39', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Krishna Shroff is the daughter of Jackie Shroff and the sister of Tiger Shroff. She is a very gorgeous and active girl and already become viral in social media. Krishna Shroff was born in 1993 in Mumbai, India as a daughter of very popular actor Jackie Shroff. In her childhood she attended the American School of Bombay with her brother, Tiger Shroff. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":336,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff-wallpaper.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Krishna Shroff Wallpaper\" class=\"wp-image-336\"/></a><figcaption>Krishna Shroff Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Krishna Shroff is currently dating a Brazilian named Spenser Johnson, a family friend of the Shroffs. She like to travel a lot and as per the popular media, she wants to travel around world. Krishna is also very much interested in Photography.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Krishna Shroff coached basketball to high school students and she is very active in other sport and athletic activities. Krishna Shroff’s boyfriend Spenser Johnson is also a sport enthusiast and a trainer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":329,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/krishna-shroff-with-tiger-shroff.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/krishna-shroff-with-tiger-shroff.jpg\" alt=\"Krishna Shroff with her brother Tiger Shroff\" class=\"wp-image-329\"/></a><figcaption>Krishna Shroff with her brother Tiger Shroff</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She has been a part of a documentary earlier, which was called the Black Sheep. The Documentary was made in the year 2015.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Krishna Shroff grabbed headlines after few pictures of her on Instagram went viral.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Krishna Shroff Photos</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[330,331,332,333,334,335],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"aligncenter\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff1.jpg\" alt=\"Krishna Shroff Hot Photo\" data-id=\"330\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/06/krishna-shroff/krishna-shroff1/#main\" class=\"wp-image-330\"/></a><figcaption>Krishna Shroff Hot Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff2.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff2.png\" alt=\"Krishna Shroff Black and White Photo\" data-id=\"331\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/06/krishna-shroff/krishna-shroff2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-331\"/></a><figcaption>Krishna Shroff Black and White Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff3.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Krishna-Shroff3.png\" alt=\"Krishna Shroff HD Photo\" data-id=\"332\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/06/krishna-shroff/krishna-shroff3/#main\" class=\"wp-image-332\"/