(316, 1, '2019-06-06 19:09:02', '2019-06-06 19:09:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pooja Bose is an Indian actress, born in 6 February 1987, in Kolkata. She is well known for playing Vrinda in the popular show Tujh Sang Preet Lagai Sajna, which was broadcast from Star Plus. Pooja Bose mainly works in Bengali movies, Bollywood Movies and Hindi TV Series &amp; reality shows. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":559,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/pooja-bose4.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/pooja-bose4.jpg\" alt=\"Pooja Bose\" class=\"wp-image-559\"/></a><figcaption>Pooja Bose</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She has also acted in a Telugu film named Veedu Theda. She made her debut in the bengali film Macho Mustanaa, with Hiran Chatterjee. She played a lead role in Raja Chanda\'s film Challenge 2, starring Dev Adhikari and Sujit Mondal\'s film Rocky. Pooja Bose Acted Few Bollywood Films her First Hindi Film Great Grand Masti in 2016 which is Very Popular in Bollywood Box office.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pooja Bose some Notable flms is Great Grand Masti, Rocky, Loveria, Teen Patti and Bhalobasa Bhalobasa 2. Pooja was also a participant in the reality dance show Jhalak Dikhla Jaa 7 as well as on Comedy Nights Bachao telecast on Colors. Her future acting offers include a negative role as a witch in Zee TV’s Qubool Hai.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Pooja Bose Photos</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[555,556,557,558,562],\"linkTo\":\"media\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/pooja-bose2.jpg\"><img src=\"htt