(318, 1, '2019-06-06 19:10:09', '2019-06-06 19:10:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rittika Sen is an popular Tollywood film actress who appears in Bengali films. She was featured in the Calcutta Times list of Most Desirable Women 2015. Rittika comes to the limelight after her movie ‘Arshinagar’, where film critics are actually appreciate her acting skills. She worked many Indian Bengali Popular Films such as Challenge 2, Masoom, Borbaad, Joi Pagla etc. Rittika Sen is very talented and one of the most popular Indian Bengali Film Actress.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":571,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen-image.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen-image.jpg\" alt=\"Rittika Sen Photo\" class=\"wp-image-571\"/></a><figcaption>Rittika Sen Photo</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rittika Sen is 26 Years Old and she was born in Kolkata, west bengal on April 14, 1991. Rittika has a younger brother. She was so much passionate about media arena from early childhood eventually turned her career into showbiz industry. Now, she is a very familiar film actress in Kolkata.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rittika Sen Debut in in bengali movie in 2012 with the movie ‘100% Love’.&nbsp; In the movie, she appeared as a child actress with Jeet and Koel Mallick. In the same year, Rittika appeared in the movie ‘Challenge 2′ with Dev and Pooja Bose. She starred in the mainstream role in the movie ‘Borbaad’ directed by Raj Chakraborty in 2014.&nbsp; In the same year, Rittika acted in the movie ‘Masoom’.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Following the year 2015, she made a career breakthrough performance in the movie ‘Arshinagar’ with superstar Dev. The movie was box office hit and the actress got the positive acclamation from the critics and audience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Rittika Sen Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[565,566,567,568,569,570],\"linkTo\":\"media\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen.png\" alt=\"Rittika Sen Photo\" data-id=\"565\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/06/rittika-sen/rittika-sen-2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-565\"/></a><figcaption>Rittika Sen Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen1.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen1.png\" alt=\"Rittika Sen Cute Photo\" data-id=\"566\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/06/rittika-sen/rittika-sen1/#main\" class=\"wp-image-566\"/></a><figcaption>Rittika Sen Cute Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen2.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen2.png\" alt=\"Rittika Sen Wallpaper\" data-id=\"567\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/06/rittika-sen/rittika-sen2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-567\"/></a><figcaption>Rittika Sen Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen3.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/rittika-sen3.png\" alt=\"Rittika Sen in Bridal Look\" data-id=\"568\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/06/rittika-sen/rittika-sen3/#main\" class=\"wp-image-568\"/></a><figcaption>Ritti