(320, 1, '2019-06-06 19:11:41', '2019-06-06 19:11:41', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Deepika Padukone is an Indian Bollywood film actress and one of the highest-paid actresses in india. She is acknowledged with several awards and rewards for her great work in Indian cinema, along with 3 filmfare awards. She is one of the most famous celebrity in India. Her name is among the list of 100 most influential people in the world in 2018 published by worlds most pronounced Time Magazine.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She was born 5 January 1986 Copenhagen, Denmark and brought up in Bangalore, India. Her father, Prakash Padukone, is a former badminton player of international repute, and her mother, Ujjala, is a travel agent. Deepika Padukone had her primary education from Sophia High School, Bengaluru and Mount Carmel College, Bengaluru.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She was appeared in a highly popular print campaign for the 2006 Kingfisher Calendar. Deepika Padukone has acted Many commercial big hit movies like Om Shanti Om (2007), Love Aaj Kal (2009), Bachna Ae Haseeno (2008), Housefull (2010), Happy New Year (2014), Cocktial, Bajirao Mastani (2015), Piku (2015), Chennai Express (2013), Jeh Jawaani hai Deewani (2013) , Padmavat (2018) etc. Deepika Padukone also appeared in a Hollywood Movie xXx: Return of Xander Cage in 2017. Padukone has been the recipient of three Filmfare Awards: Best Female Debut for Om Shanti Om (2007), and two Best Actress awards for Goliyon Ki Raasleela Ram-Leela (2013) and Piku (2015). Deepika Padukone has been the recipient of three Filmfare Awards: Best Female Debut for Om Shanti Om (2007), and two Best Actress awards for Goliyon Ki Raasleela Ram-Leela (2013) and Piku (2015).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition to acting, Deepika Padukone has written opinion columns and has been involved with women\'s health and fitness magazines. She has also supported charitable organisations, and has performed for stage shows.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Deepika Padukone', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'deepika-padukone', '', '', '2019-08-15 19:58:08', '2019-08-15 19:58:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=320', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(324, 1, '2019-06-07 13:26:34', '2019-06-07 13:26:34', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Priyanka Chopra is an Indian Film Actress, Singer, Model, Film Produer and Philanthropist. She was born on 18 July 1982 in Jamshedpur, Jharkhand, India. Her parents are Ashok and Madhu Chopra, both physicians in the Indian Army. Priyanka Chopra works in Bollywood Film Industry and few Tamil, Telugu, Hollywood Movies. She was made her screen debut in Hindi Movie The Hero (2003). Due to her parents\' occupations the family relocated to a number of places in India, including Delhi, Chandigarh, Ambala, Ladakh, Lucknow, Bareilly, and Pune. Among the schools she attended were La Martiniere Girls\' School in Lucknow and St. Maria Goretti College in Bareilly. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At the age of thirteen, Chopra moved to the United States to study, living with her aunt, and attending schools in Newton, Massachusetts, and Cedar Rapids, Iowa, after a stop in Queens, New York, as her aunt\'s family also moved frequently. She was especially close to her father, who died in June 2013; in 2012, she got a tattoo reading \"Daddy\'s lil girl\", in his handwriting.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She is the winner of the Miss India and Miss World beauty pageants in 2000. Though, she wanted to make her career in criminal psychology, after winning the Miss India contest, she dropped the idea as she was getting many film offers. Priyanka Chopra worked many commercial successful popular films such as Andaasz (2003), Mujhse Shaadi Karogi (2004), Fashion (2008), 7 Khoon aaf (2011), Barfi! (2012), Mary Kom (2014), Dil Dhadakne Do (2015), Bajirao Mastani (2015), etc. She is now Highest-paid Bollywood Actress. She earn 9-10 Crore per hindi movie in India. Abhishek Bachchan, who gave her the name \"Piggy Chops\" during the shooting of the film Bluffmaster. She won the National Award – Best Actress for her film ‘Fashion’ (2008).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Controversies </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>After the rumors of her alleged affair with Akshay Kumar, she and Akshay Kumar mutually decided not to work together after Waqt.</li><li>Her alleged affair with Shah Rukh Khan created a lot of fire. It all incepted when Shah Rukh started giving special treatment to Priyanka recommending her to filmmakers to cast her in the film. Also, her regular visits to Shah Rukh\'s house Mannat and also at various other events, and to meet his wife Gauri Khan. After all these sequence of incidents, Gauri made it clear that she didn\'t want her husband to work with Priyanka anymore, and as a result, both stopped working with each other. </li><li>After she shared her photo on the cover of Maxim India where the actor looked flawless, it went viral, not because of her beauty but her armpits that many thought looked photoshopped without any underarm wrinkles.</li><li>She had a twitter battle with comedian Tanmay Bhat after he mocked her accent just like many others on social media. “When I say @priyankachopra’s name in my head I now automatically pronounce it like “Priyaaaanka Chopruh”,” he tweeted. </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Priyanka Chopra', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'priyanka-chopra', '', '', '2019-08-16 05:28:27', '2019-08-16 05:28:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=324', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(326, 1, '2019-06-07 13:32:32', '2019-06-07 13:32:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kareena Kapoor is an Indian actress who appears in Hindi films. She is the daughter of actors Randhir Kapoor and Babita and younger sister of Karishma Kapoor. She is the paternal granddaughter of actor and filmmaker Raj Kapoor, maternal granddaughter of actor Hari Shivdasani, and niece of actor Rishi Kapoor. She was born in Born on 21 September 1980. According to Kapoor, the name \"Kareena\" was derived from the book Anna Karenina, which her mother read while she was pregnant with her. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She debuted with Abhishek Bachchan in J. P. Dutta\'s war drama Refugee. Refugee was a moderate box-office success in India and Kapoor\'s performance earned her the Filmfare Award for Best Female Debut. Kareena Kapoor is the recipient of several awards, including six Filmfare Awards, and is one of Bollywood\'s most popular and highest-paid actresses. A key point in her career came when she was cast by Karan Johar in Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham as Pooja in the 2001.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Her outstanding acting in the film Jab We Met (2007) as Geet, brought success and fan following, also appreciate by film critics. She won several awards for her performance in this movie, including her second Screen Award and the Filmfare Award for Best Actress. She has her wax statues in England and Singapore’s Madame Tussauds Museum.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On 16 October 2012, Kapoor married actor Saif Ali Khan in a private ceremony in Bandra, Mumbai. On 20 December 2016, Kapoor gave birth to her son, Taimur Ali Khan Pataudi, at Breach Candy Hospital in Mumbai.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Controversies </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>There had been her catfights with Bipasha Basu on the sets of the film Ajnabee , as she publicly took a dig at her skin tone by calling her a \"kali billi.\"</li><li>Her and Shahid Kapoor\'s controversial MMS having a steamy liplock, which went viral all over media.</li><li>She publicly made fun of Priyanka Chopra\'s accent, after which Priyanka finally replied by saying that she got it from the same place that Saif got his from.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Kareena Kapoor', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kareena-kapoor', '', '', '2019-08-16 05:31:11', '2019-08-16 05:31:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=326', 0, 'post', '', 0),
