(340, 1, '2019-06-13 19:50:09', '2019-06-13 19:50:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Katrina Kaif is a British Indian Film Actress and Model. She has a huge fan following in Bollywood film industry and is one of India\'s highest-paid actresses. At the age of fourteen, Katrina Kaif won a beauty contest in Hawaii. She was debuted in Indian movie with English-Hindi erotic heist film Boom with Amitabh Bachchan. Boom (2003) had its first screening at the Cannes Film Festival, and was heavily promoted at the event.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":584,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif2.jpg\" alt=\"Katrina Kaif Photo\" class=\"wp-image-584\"/></a><figcaption>Katrina Kaif Photo</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Katrina Kaif\'s nickname is Kat. She was born on 16 July 1983 in Hong Kong. Hence, her current age is [DateCounter startDate=\"1983-07-16\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years. Katrina\'s Zodiac is Cancer. She is in several countries before she moved to London. Katrina is Muslim by Religion and Nationality is British.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>174 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Meters</td><td>1.74 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Feet Inches</td><td>5\' 8\"</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>56 Kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds </td><td>123 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Shoe Size</td><td>8 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Dress Size</td><td>6 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Brown</td></tr><tr><td>Body Measurements</td><td>34-26-34</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family Members </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Katrina\'s father name is Mohammed Kaif who is a British businessman of Kashmiri Indian descent. Her mother name is Suzanne Turquotte(also spelt Susanna) who is an English lawyer and charity worker. She has one elder brother Michael Kaif and six sisters named, Stephanie, Christine, Natasha, Melissa, Sonia and Isabel. Due to their frequent relocation, Katrina Kaif and her siblings never went to any school and they were home-schooled by a series of tutors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":588,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif-family.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif-family.jpg\" alt=\"Katrina Kaif family\" class=\"wp-image-588\"/></a><figcaption>Katrina Kaif family</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Boys, affairs, spouse name </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Katrina’s personal life is always an interesting subject to media and Bollywood lovers. In stating of her career she was in a relationship with Salman Khan. They had breakup in 2010 and Katrina Kaif calling it her \"first serious relationship\". She falls in love with Ranbir Kapoor during the filming of Ajab Prem Ki Ghazab Kahani. Her current relationship status is Unmarried.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Favourite Things and Hobbies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Favourite Food</td><td>Yorkshire pudding, cheesecake, kheer, cinnamon rolls, steamed fish, lamb chops with salad &amp; baby potatoes, grilled vegetables</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actor</td><td>Hrithik Roshan, Leonardo DiCaprio, Johnny Depp and Robert Pattinson</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actress</td><td>Penelope Cruz, Madhuri Dixit and Kajol</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Musician</td><td>Radiohead, Muse, Coldplay</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Song</td><td>Moon by Poolside</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Book</td><td>All books by Sidney Sheldon</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Colours</td><td>Pink, White, Mauve</td></tr><tr><td>Favorite Movie Bollywood Films</td><td>Umrao Jaan, Dil Dhadakne Do, Tanu Weds Manu Returns</td></tr><tr><td>Favorite Hollywood Films</td><td>Casablanca, Gone with the Wind</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Sport</td><td>Cricket, Chess</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Perfumes</td><td>Narciso Rodriguez For Her</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Destination</td><td>London, Italy, Spain, Dubai and Havana</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Restaurants</td><td>Mainland China, and Wasabi by Morimoto at The Taj Mahal Palace Hotel in Mumbai, Hakkasan, Harrods Georgian Restaurant, Alloro, Aqua Kyoto in London.</td></tr><tr><td>Hobbies</td><td>Travelling, playing chess, painting and reading</td></tr><tr><td>Best Friend</td><td>Director Kabir Khan</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Katrina Kaif filmography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Katrina Kaif works in Bollywood Film Industry and few Telugu, Malayalam Movies. She worked many commercial successful movies such as New York, Ajab Prem Ki Ghazab Kahani, Raajneeti, Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara, Mere Brother Ki Dulhan, Ek Tha Tiger, Dhoom 3, Bang Bang etc. Kaif’s career prospects changed in 2007, when she appeared in four Bollywood hits. Katrina Kaif is the recipient of several awards, including “BIG Star Entertainment Awards”, “Screen Awards”, “Star Guild Awards”, “Stardust Awards”, “Zee Cine Awards” etc. for her contribution in Indian Film Industry. Kaif’s highest-grossing films Ek Tha Tiger (2012), Dhoom 3 (2013) and ‘Tiger Zinda Hai’ (2017) rank among the highest-grossing Indian films of all time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":585,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif.jpg\" alt=\"Katrina Kaif  in Red Dress\" class=\"wp-image-585\"/></a><figcaption>Katrina Kaif  in Red Dress</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salary and Net Worth</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Katrina’s immovable property amounting to Rs.142 crore. Her annual income is Rs 29 crore from movies and various brand endorsement. Katrina owns many expensive cars like Audi Q3, Mercedes ML350, Audi Q7. She owns a Bunglow in Hampstead, London worth Rs 7.02 crore. Furthermore, she has 3 BHK Apartment in Bandra, Apartment in Lokhandwala and one Penthouse in Bandra.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education and School, College</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Katrina has home schooling (Taught at home by her mother, tutors and also did correspondence courses)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact Address   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>House Address</td><td>B-09 &amp; G-10, Ground Floor, Mourya House, Next to V.I.P. Plaza, New Link Road, Andheri West, Mumbai, Maharashtra 400053, India</td></tr><tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>She didn\'t like share her Phone number to publicly.</td></tr><tr><td>Email Id</td><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/KatrinaKaif/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/KatrinaKaifFB</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/katrinakaif/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katrina_Kaif</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Facts about Katrina Kaif</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":586,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif-in-boom.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/katrina-kaif-in-boom.jpg\" alt=\"Katrina Kaif in Boom\" class=\"wp-image-586\"/></a><figcaption>Katrina Kaif in Boom\n\n</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Katrina Kaif also helps her mom in charitable activities and also she endorses one of the biggest brands in the world.</li><li>Her personal photos with Ex-boyfriend Ranbir Kapoor were leaked on internet during their trip to Ibiza.</li><li>During the shooting of the film Namastey London, Katrina went to Ajmer Sharif dargah in short skirt that hurt people’s religious sentiments.</li><li>Before New York, Katrina Kaif’s voice was dubbed over by voice artists in most of her films due to her lack of fluency in Hindi and other Indian languages.</li><li>Although she appeared in a series of successful films, critics noted that she had little to do in them as they were generally male-dominated.</li><li>She is the first Bollywood actress to have a Barbie doll crafted in her image.</li><li>Ayesha Shroff, wife of Jackie Shroff and the producer of her debut film Boom changed her second name from Turquotte to Kaif, as she thought that it was not catchy and is difficult to pronounce.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"l