(342, 1, '2019-06-13 19:53:02', '2019-06-13 19:53:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Sharma is an Indian Film Actress, Model and Film Producer. She is a very popular Bollywood Film Actress. she is currently one of the leading &amp; commercial successful and one of the Highest-paid Actress of Bollywood. Anushka Sharma has received Several accolades including one Filmfare Award from Seven Nomination. She was made her debut with Shahrukh Khan blockbuster Hit film Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi (2008), which won her Filmfare Best Actress Award. She had her biggest commercial successes with the roles of a television reporter in the religious satire PK (2014) and a wrestler in the sports drama Sultan (2016), both of which rank among the highest-grossing Indian films.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":606,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma Photoshoot\" class=\"wp-image-606\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma Photoshoot</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Sharma\'s nickname is Anu and Nushie. She was born on <strong>1 May 1988</strong> in Ayodhya, Uttar Pradesh, India. Hence, her current age is <strong>[DateCounter startDate=\"1988-05-01\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years</strong>. Anushka\'s Zodiac is Taurus. She basically belongs to Ayodhya, Uttar Pradesh but she grew up in Bengaluru and now she is settled in Mumbai.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>175 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Meters</td><td>1.75 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Feet Inches</td><td>5\' 9\"</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>55 Kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds </td><td>121 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Shoe Size</td><td>8 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Dress Size</td><td>6 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Hazel Brown</td></tr><tr><td>Body Measurements</td><td>34-26-34</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family Members </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka\'S father, Colonel Ajay Kumar Sharma, is an army officer. Her mother Ashima Sharma, is a homemaker. Her brother name is Karnesh Sharma who is working in Merchant Navy. She was raised in Bangalore.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Boys, affairs, spouse name </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":607,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma_virat_kohli.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma_virat_kohli.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma with Virat Kohli\" class=\"wp-image-607\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma with Virat Kohli</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Sharma is Married to Cricketer Virat Kohli in 11 December 2017. Actress Anushka Sharma and Virat kohli has affair for a long time and they got married in December 2017. Before that, Anushka had affairs with Zoheb Yusuf when she came to mumbai and started her modeling career. Also, She dated Ranveer Singh during the shooting of Band Baaja Baaraat in 2010.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Favourite Things and Hobbies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Favourite Food</td><td>khichoni — a soup with onions and tomatoes as base, Kakori Seekh Kebab</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actor</td><td>Shah Rukh Khan</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actress</td><td>Rani Mukerji</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Musician</td><td>A.R. Rahman</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Song</td><td>Chanda Re Chanda Re</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Car</td><td>Range Rover Vogue SUV</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Book</td><td>\'Open\' by Andre Agassi</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Colours</td><td>White, Grey, Black, Navy blue</td></tr><tr><td>Favorite Movie Bollywood Films</td><td>Jab We Met, Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge, Chak De! India and Dil Se</td></tr><tr><td>Favorite Hollywood Films</td><td>The Shawshank Redemption, Life Is Beautiful, In the Mood for Love, Fish Tank </td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Sport</td><td>Cricket</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Perfumes</td><td>Ralph Lauren Blue, Dolce and Gabbana’s Light Blue</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Destination</td><td>The Himalayas, Goa</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Restaurants</td><td>Samarpan in Bengaluru, Café Piccolo in Bangalore</td></tr><tr><td>Hobbies</td><td>Dancing, Reading</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Anushka Sharma filmography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She was made her debut with Shahrukh Khan blockbuster Hit film Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi (2008), which won her Filmfare Best Actress Award. She had her biggest commercial successes with the roles of a television reporter in the religious satire PK (2014) and a wrestler in the sports drama Sultan (2016), both of which rank among the highest-grossing Indian films. Anushka Sharma’s other  commercially successful popular movie are Band Baaja Baaraat (2010), Jab Tak Hai Jaan (2012), NH10 (2015), Ae Dil Hai Mushkil (2016), Sanju which is Sanjay Dutt Biopic (2018) etc. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><th>Movie name</th><th>Year</th></tr><tr><td>Zero</td><td>2018</td></tr><tr><td>Sui Dhaaga: Made in India </td><td>2018</td></tr><tr><td>Sanju </td><td>2018</td></tr><tr><td>Pari </td><td>2018</td></tr><tr><td>Jab Harry Met Sejal </td><td>2017</td></tr><tr><td>Phillauri </td><td>2017</td></tr><tr><td>Ae Dil Hai Mushkil </td><td>2016</td></tr><tr><td>Sultan </td><td>2016</td></tr><tr><td>Dil Dhadakne Do </td><td>2015</td></tr><tr><td>Bombay Velvet </td><td>2015</td></tr><tr><td>NH10 </td><td>2015</td></tr><tr><td>PK </td><td>2014</td></tr><tr><td>Matru ki Bijlee ka Mandola </td><td>2013</td></tr><tr><td>Jab Tak Hai Jaan</td><td>2012</td></tr><tr><td>Ladies vs. Ricky Bahl</td><td>2011</td></tr><tr><td>Patiala House</td><td>2011</td></tr><tr><td>Band Baaja Baaraat </td><td>2010</td></tr><tr><td>Badmaash Company</td><td>2010</td></tr><tr><td>Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi </td><td>2008</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salary and Net Worth</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka’s immovable property amounting to Rs.107 crore. Her annual income is Rs 29 crore from movies and various brand endorsement. She asked Rs.10-12 for movie. Anushka owns many expensive cars like a black Range Rover Sport SUV, a black Mercedes and two of luxury cars from brands like Audi and BMW. She owns a 3BHK flat at Panch Vatika in Yari Road. Furthermore, she has 3 BHK Apartment Badrinath Towers, Andheri, Mumbai.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":632,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-in-Range-Rover.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-in-Range-Rover.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma in her Range Rover Vogue SUV\" class=\"wp-image-632\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma in her Range Rover Vogue SUV</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education and School, College</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Sharma was educated at the Army School, Bengaluru. She was a topper in school. She had received a degree in arts from Mount Carmel College in Bangalore. Anushka completed her Master Degree Program in Economics through correspondence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact Address   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>House Address</td><td>Badrinath Towers, 20th Floor, Seven Bungalows, Andheri, Mumbai. 3BHK flat at Panch Vatika apartments in Yari Road. </td></tr><tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>She didn\'t like share her Phone number to publicly.</td></tr><tr><td>Email Id</td><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/AnushkaSharmaOfficial/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/AnushkaSharma</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/anushkasharma/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anushka_Sharma</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Facts about Anushka Sharma</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Anushka started her modeling career at the Lakme Fashion Week as a model for Wendell Rodricks\'s Les Vamps Show</li><li>Her first ramp walk was at the age of 15.</li><li>She late riser and like to have egg and a glass of fresh juice in breakfast</li><li>Anushka works out 4 times a week and has personal trainer.</li><li>Anushka is a beer drinker.</li><li>While paying her homage to Late Dr APJ Abdul Kalam on twitter, she misspelled his name as \"ABJ Kalam Azad\". After it, she was criticized on twitter and she deleted that tweet and posted another one, which was again wrong as she wrote \"APJ Kalam Azad\". At the third attempt, she finally tweeted it correctly i.e. \"Dr. APJ Abdul Kalam\".</li><li>There was a rift in her relationship with Virat Kohli for a while in the early 2016. If reports are to be believed then the reason behind it was that Virat invested a good amount of money in Anushka\'s film Bombay Velvet, which unfortunately failed at the box office. And, when Virat asked about the money loss to Anushka, she felt upset. Virat even unfollowed her on Twitter and Instagram, but after few months they got back together.</li><li>Apart from acting, Sharma supports a number of charities and causes. She walked the ramp to support Shabana Azmi’s Mijwan Welfare Society, an NGO that helps empower women.</li><li>She supports various charities and causes, including gender equality and animal rights, and is the co-founder of the production company Clean Slate Films. </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Anushka Sharma Photos</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[608,622,624,625,626,627,628],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"aligncenter\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma2.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma HD Wallpaper\" data-id=\"608\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-608\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma HD Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-candid-photoshoot.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-candid-photoshoot.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma Candid Photo-shoot\" data-id=\"622\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma-candid-photoshoot/#main\" class=\"wp-image-622\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma Candid Photo-shoot</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-2.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma Photo\" data-id=\"624\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma-2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-624\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-lehenga.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-lehenga.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma in lehenga\" data-id=\"625\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma-lehenga/#main\" class=\"wp-image-625\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma in lehenga</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma_HD_photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma_HD_photo.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma HD Photo\" data-id=\"626\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma_hd_photo/#main\" class=\"wp-image-626\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma HD Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-photoshoot.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-photoshoot.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma photoshoot\" data-id=\"627\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma-photoshoot/#main\" class=\"wp-image-627\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma photoshoot</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma_Cute_Photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma_Cute_Photo.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma Cute Photo\" data-id=\"628\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma_cute_photo/#main\" class=\"wp-image-628\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma Cute Photo</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->', 'Anushka Sharma Height | Weight | Age | Biography | Wiki | Husband | Family', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'anushka-sharma', '', '', '2019-10-08 20:13:58', '2019-10-08 20:13:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost/bollywikia/?p=342', 0, 'post', '', 0);
