(348, 1, '2019-06-13 20:02:36', '2019-06-13 20:02:36', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Shetty is an Indian actress, Model and former Yoga Teacher who is working in Telugu and Tamil films. Her actual name is Anushka Shetty. She was born 7 November 1981 in Puttur, Mangalore, Karnataka, India. Anushka\'s Shetty Father name is A.N. Vittal Shetty and her mother is Prafulla Shetty. She has two brother Gunaranjan Shetty who is a businessman and Sai Ramesh Shetty who is a doctor. Anushka did her Bachelor of Computer Applications at the Mount Carmel College, Bangalore.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka made her on screen debut in 2005 with Telugu Movie Super. Anushka Shetty is now one of the leading &amp; commercial successful film actress in telegu film industry. She ger her first Filmfare Award for Best Actress – Telugu, Nandi Award, Cinemaa Award for Best Actress for her dual roles in the dark fantasy Arundhati. She got her first success with ‘Vikramarkudu’ (2006), opposite Ravi Teja.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She worked in a blockbuster Film Baahubali 2: The Conclusion in 2017, where shy played Maharai Devasena. This film is all time Blockbuster and crossed 1000 crores in Worldwide box office collection in just 10 Days. She is the only actress to have worked with S.S. Rajamouli for more than once.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/anushkashettyofficial/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/AnushkaShetty/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/anushka_asf?lang=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anushka_Shetty</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Anushka Shetty Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n