(350, 1, '2019-06-13 20:04:05', '2019-06-13 20:04:05', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Shruti Haasan is an Indian Film Actress, Model and Singer. She was born on 28 January 1986 in Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India. She is the daughter of Actor &amp; Film-maker Kamal Haasan and Sarika Thakur. Her father is a Tamil, while her mother Sarika was born to a Maharashtrian father and Rajput mother. Her younger sister Akshara Haasan is also an actress and represented India nationally for Ballroom Latin dancing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a child artist, Haasan sang in films and appeared in a guest role in her father\'s Hey Ram (2000). She was made her lead role debut movie Luck in 2009 with actors Imran Khan. She made her Telugu debut in January 2011, acting opposite Siddharth in the fantasy adventure film Anaganaga O Dheerudu, directed by Prakash Kovelamudi, son of director K. Raghavendra Rao. The film, co-produced by Walt Disney Pictures. Shruti Haasan was payed lead role for Aishwarya Dhanush\'s directorial debut 3, a romantic drama film co-starring Dhanush. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Shruti Haasan has received three Filmfare Awards and has established herself as one of the leading actresses of South Indian cinema. Shruti Haasan made her singing debut “Potri Paadadi Ponne” song for the film Thevar Magan (1992, Tamil). She is Highest-paid South Indian Actress. Shruti Haasan was signed as a brand ambassador for the electrical appliance company Lloyd and also Brand Ambassador for Fossil Watches in India. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/ShrutiHaasan/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/shrutihaasan</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/shrutzhaasan/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://