(363, 1, '2019-06-14 19:06:00', '2019-06-14 19:06:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Simran Kaur Mundi is an Indian Film Actress and Model. She was born on 13 September 1988 in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. She is from a Jat Sikh family her ancestors are from Mundian Jattan, Hoshiarpur, Punjab. She studied from the boarding school Scindia Kanya Vidyalaya, Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh. She completed her Bio-Technology degree from the Holkar College of Science Indore in 2007. She is winner of Miss India Universe 2008 in Mumbai on 5 April 2008.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She represented India at Miss Universe 2008 held in Vietnam and placed in various preliminary events, she was one of the top five finalists at the Best in Swimsuit round. Simran has her on-screen debut with Hindi Film Jo Hum Chahein (2011) and Her Punjabi Debut Best of Luck (2013). She was shared the screen opposite comedian Kapil Sharma who made his acting debut in the film Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon directed by Abbas Mustan.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/SimrankMundiOfficial/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/SimrankMundi</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/simrankaurmundi/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simran_Kaur_Mundi</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Simran Kaur Mundi Photos</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[715,716,717,718,719,720],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"aligncenter\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/simran-kaur-mundi.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywi