(366, 1, '2019-06-14 19:06:51', '2019-06-14 19:06:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yumna Zaidi is a Pakistani Actress. Yumna is a daughter of Zameendar Zaidi and Shabana Naheed Zaidi. Yumna has 2 elder sisters, who are married and one younger brother. She lives in Texas and works in between Karachi-Lahore.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She was born on 30 July 1989 in Lahore, Pakistan. She mainly works in Pakistani Television Serials. She has done a masters in interior designing and she started her career as RJ.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yumna Zaidi was made her on-screen debut with ARY Digital serial ‘Thakan’ (2012). She became popular for her worked in TV Series like, Khushi Ek Roag, Meri Dulari, Dil Mohally Ki Haveli, Mausam, Guzaarish, Jugnoo, Yeh Raha Dil, Pukaar etc. Yumna Zaidi is currently working on Hum TV Serial Dar Si Jati Hai Sila since 2017 to present.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She recipient four Hum Awards for Best Actress, Supporting Actress and Best Villain role Award. Yumna Zaidi is looking so pretty, stylish, talented and most popular for her mind blowing acting.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/YumnaZaidi.Official/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/yumnazaidireal?lang=en</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/yumnazaidiofficial/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yumna_Zaidi</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Yumna Zaidi Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[725,726,727,728,729,730],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"aligncenter\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"