(370, 1, '2019-06-14 19:09:14', '2019-06-14 19:09:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bala Hijam is a Manipuri actress, who predominantly appears in Manipuri and South Indian movie. Her is basically from Imphal, Manipur, India. Her mother is a housewife.\' As for her father runs a small business of his own. She has four brothers and sisters. she has an elder sister, a younger sister and a younger brother. she\'s the second eldest among her siblings.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bala Hijam works in Tamil, Telugu, Malayalam and Kannada Film Industry. She was made her screen debut in Film Imagi Laman Singamdre (2010) as Niti. She is working Many Films in different Languages. She has also acted in one Malayalam thriller road film, named Neelakasham Pachakadal Chuvanna Bhoomi. Bala Hijam\'s recent project is Mr. Khadang in 2017. Bala Hijam started shooting for her Bollywood debut Zindagi on the Rocks but was left incomplete due to some issues.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bala Hijam won the Best Actress Award at 8th Manipur State Film Festival, 2013 for the film Yaiskulgee Pakhang Angaoba. She acquired pan-Indian success in 2013.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Bala Hijam Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[762,763,764,765,766,767],\"linkTo\":\"media\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/bala-hijam.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/bala-hijam.jpg\" alt=\"Bala Hijam Photo\" data-id=\"762\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/14/bala-hijam/bala-hijam-2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-762\"/></a><figcaption>Bala Hijam Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/bala-hijam3.jpg\"><img src=\