(372, 1, '2019-06-14 19:10:02', '2019-06-14 19:10:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ritabhari Chakraborty is an Indian Bengali film and television actress. She was born on June 26, 1992 in kolkata. Ritabhari Chakraborty brought up in Kolkata and started her career early in modelling and television at the age of 15. She finished her schooling from Hariyana Vidya Mandir. She topped in History and Bengali all over India in CBSE exams in the year 2011. She graduated in History from Jadavpur University in the year 2014.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ritabhari Chakraborty is Featured in numerous magazines and advertisements, she is quite well known in the advertising industry as well and has endorsed more than 100 brands like Chandrani Pearls, Rupayan Jewellers, Shehnaz, Rajlaxmi Jewellers etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ritabhari Chakraborty and her mother runs an NGO \"Scud Society for Social Communication “ which primarily focuses on the development of women in rural areas in West Bengal (currently involved with Bashtala) . She was the ambassador of the Dog Owners and Lovers association (DOLA) and is also known for her charitable works for the \"Ideal school for the deaf\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She made her first appearance in television as the female protagonist of the popular Indian Bengali television serial Ogo Bodhu Sundari. In 2011, she was reported to be making her big screen debut in Tomar Shange Praner Khela. Her first Hindi film was \"Pari\" which released on March 2,2018 and also stars Anushka Sharma.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ritabhari played the female protagonist in the Bengali television serial Ogo Bodhu Sundari. The serial was remade into Hindi as Sasural Genda Phool. In 2011, she made her big screen debut with the film Tomar Shange Praner Khela. The film was directed by Rakesh Kumar, who also directed Sasural Genda Phool. The story of the film explores the relationship of the female protagonist with five men. Later she worked in other films like Barood and Tobu Basanta.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She recipient Star Jalsha Entertainment Awards, Protidin Tele Somman and Uttar Kumar Kala Ratna Awards for Best Actor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Apart from her acting career she is also known for topping ISC exams in History and Bengali in the year 2011.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Ritabhari Chakraborty Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[772,773,774,775,776,777]} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ritabhari-chakraborty.jpg\" alt=\"Ritabhari Chakraborty Photo\" data-id=\"772\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/14/ritabhari-chakraborty/ritabhari-chakraborty-2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-772\"/><figcaption>Ritabhari Chakraborty Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ritabhari-chakraborty2.jpg\" alt=\"Ritabhari Chakraborty Hot Photo\" data-id=\"773\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/14/ritabhari-chakraborty/ritabhari-chakraborty2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-773\"/><figcaption>Ritabhari Chakraborty Hot Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/ritabhari-chakraborty3.jpg\" alt=\"Ritabhari Chakraborty Cute Photo\" data-id=\"774\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/14/ritabhari-chakraborty/ritabhari-chakraborty3/#main\" class=\"wp-image-774\"/><figcaption>Ritabhari Chakraborty Cute Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localh