(379, 1, '2019-06-16 19:11:53', '2019-06-16 19:11:53', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Zoya Afroz, (born January 10, 1994) is an Indian actress and model who appears in Hindi, Punjabi movies and television serials. She was born on 10 January 1994 in Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh India. She has done her schooling from R N Shah High School, and attended Mithibai College in Vile parle Mumbai, for her graduation. Her Father name is Shadaab Afroz and Her Mother is Saleha Afroz. She has a brother named Zaf Khan. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Zoya Afroz started her career when she was 3 years old. She got her break from Rasna Mahasearch Contest at the age of 3 after which she did the TV commercial for the same. She has also worked on other TV commercials like Whirlpool, Shoppers stop, Jet Airways, PSPO fan and New York Life Insurance, as a child artist. She has acted with many celebrities like Karishma Kapoor, Saif Ali Khan, Salman Khan and Sonali Bendre in the film Hum Saath Saath Hain and also with Aishwarya Rai Bachchan and Abhishek Bacchan in the film Kuch Naa Kaho.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Zoya Afroz was the winner of Pond\'s Femina Miss India Indore 2013 Crown. She was later crowned as Pond’s Femina Miss India International 2013 at the 50th edition of Pond’s Femina Miss India 2013 that was held in Yash Raj Studio, Mumbai on March 24, 2013.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/zoyaafrozofficiall/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/zoyaafroz?lang=en</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/zoyaafroz/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zoya_Afroz</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Zoya Afroz Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp: