(402, 1, '2019-06-16 19:25:08', '2019-06-16 19:25:08', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Janhvi Kapoor is an Indian bollywood Actress. She is a start kid and She is the elder daughter of famous Bollywood actress Sridevi and film producer Boney Kapoor. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Janhvi Kapoor\'s nickname is Janhvi. She was born on 7 March 1997 in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. Hence, her current age is [DateCounter startDate=\"1997-03-07\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years. Janhvi Kapoor\'s Zodiac is Pisces. Her hometown is in Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Janhvi is 5′ 4” tall &amp; weighs approx. 50 kg. She has been god gifted with dark brown eyes, fair complexion &amp; a sexy body.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>163 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in meters</td><td>1.63 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Inches</td><td>5’ 4”</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>50 kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds</td><td>110 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family and Relatives</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1874,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Jhanvi-Kapoor-Sridevi.jpg\" alt=\"Janhvi Kapoor with her mother Sridevi\" class=\"wp-image-1874\"/><figcaption>Janhvi Kapoor with her mother Sridevi</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Father</td><td>Boney Kapoor, Film producer</td></tr><tr><td>Mother</td><td>Late Sridevi, Actress</td></tr><tr><td>Brother</td><td>Arjun Kapoor (Half brother)</td></tr><tr><td>Sisters</td><td>Khushi Kapoor, Anshula Kapoor (Half sister)</td></tr><tr><td>Religion</td><td>Hinduism</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Affairs, Boyfriends and Marital Status</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Janhvi Kapoor is in a relationship and dating Shikhar Pahariya who is the maternal grandchild of famous politician Sushil Kumar Shinde and son of Mumbai-based businessman Sanjay Pahariya. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Later on, she had a relationship with Akshat Rajan, who is an Entrepreneur. In August 2016, her personal pictures with her boyfriend Akshat Rajan were leaked on social media in which both are kissing. The photos were taken during a late-night party in a nightclub.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1872,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Janhvi-Kapoor-kiss.jpg\" alt=\"Janhvi Kapoor and Akshat Rajan\" class=\"wp-image-1872\"/><figcaption>Janhvi Kapoor and Akshat Rajan</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is a rumours that Janhvi Kapoor now dating with her co-star from movie Dhadak, Ishaan Khatter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"videoWrapper\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jkDneCeEisc\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education and School, College   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Janhvi Kapoor She completed her school education at Dhirubhai Ambani International School, Mumbai. Completed her training in acting along with Shahrukh Khan‘s son Aryan Khan is undergoing from a Film Institute in USA named ‘The Lee Strasberg Theatre &amp; Film Institute’.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Favorites Things and Like &amp; Dislike   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Favorite Actor</td><td>Shah Rukh Khan, Hrithik Roshan, Ranveer Singh</td></tr><tr><td>Favorite Actress</td><td>Deepika Padukone, Priyanka Chopra</td></tr><tr><td>Favorite Color</td><td>Pink</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Singer</td><td>Enrique Iglesias, David Guetta</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Author</td><td>Paulo Coelho</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Food</td><td>Rogan josh</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Movie</td><td>Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Fashion Designer</td><td>Manish Malhotra</td></tr><tr><td>Hobbies</td><td>Travelling, listening to music</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Money Factor   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Janhvi Kapoor received Rs 60 lakh for her debut movie Dhadak. Her net worth is ₹150 Crore.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact Address   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>House Address</td><td>An apartment in Lokhandwala Complex, Andheri, North West, Mumbai</td></tr><tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>Not Available</td></tr><tr><td>Email Id</td><td>janhvi.kapoor@gmail.com </td></tr><tr><td>Website</td><td>Not Available</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Filmography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>She made Bollywood Debut with Actor Ishaan Khattar in the upcoming movie Dhadak… Ishaan Khattar is the half-brother of actor Shahid Kapoor. Dhadak is a remake of the 2016 Marathi film Sairat.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1873,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/dhadak-Janhvi-Kapoor.jpg\" alt=\"Dhadak poster - Janhvi Kapoor and Ishaan Khattar\" class=\"wp-image-1873\"/><figcaption>Dhadak poster - Janhvi Kapoor and Ishaan Khattar</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Dhadak</td><td>2018</td></tr><tr><td>Gunjan Saxena</td><td>2020</td></tr><tr><td>Roohi Afza</td><td>2020</td></tr><tr><td>Ghost Stories</td><td>2020</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Awards &amp; Recognition</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Janhvi Kapoor won the Zee Cine Award for Best Female Debut.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Facts about Janhvi Kapoor</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>In 2015, Jhanvi was offered a role opposite Telugu superstar Mahesh Babu, but she declined it due to a large age gap with Mahesh.</li><li>Her mother Sridevi never want that Jhanvi is goint join Bollywood. Instead, she wanted Jhanvi to get married and settle down. Butlater on she get convinced.</li><li>She was the first choice for the film ‘Simmba’ opposite Ranveer Singh, but she declined the offer; as she was quite nervous about acting with such a big star.</li><li>On 24 February 2018, while attending a wedding function in Dubai, Jhanvi\'s mother Sridevi died of an accidental drowning. It was just before the release of her debut movie Dhadak.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/janhvikapoor/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/JanhviKapoorfanspage