<h3>Favourite Things</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Favourite Food</td><td>Cooking Bengali and Chinese dishes</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actor</td><td>Uttam Kumar, Amitabh Bachan, Richard Gere</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actress</td><td>Aparna Sen, Rekha, Julia Roberts</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Movies</td><td>Silsila, Andhi, Devdas, Pather Panchali, Saatpaake Bandha, Nimantron, Meghe Dhaka Tara, Sedin Chaitra Mas, Pretty Woman, Towering Inferno, Titanic</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Singer</td><td>Shaan, Sonu Nigam, Raghav,Srikanto, Shreya, Sunidhi, Lopamundra &amp; legends Kishore Kumar, Md. Rafi, LataMangeshker, AshoBhosle</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Author</td><td>Rabindranath Tagore</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Color</td><td>All the colors of rainbow</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Dress</td><td>Saree, lahenga, Indo-western attire</td></tr><tr><td>Hobbies</td><td>Gardening, Travelling</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salary and Net Worth</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Indrani Dutta is having a triplex flat, that is the third and fourth floors as well as the terrace in a building near the Tolly Club, Kolkata. Her estimated net worth of almost $5 million. She earns almost Rs.20 Lacs to Rs.20 Lacs for every movie she plays.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education and School, College</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Indrani Dutta has completed her schooling from Kamala Girls’ High School, Kolkata. Later on completed her Graduation in Arts from Sivanath Sastri College, Kolkata, India..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact Address   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>House Address</td><td>South Calcutta (near the Tolly Club), Kolkata </td></tr><tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>S