(439, 1, '2019-06-18 18:57:32', '2019-06-18 18:57:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel Mallick (কোয়েল মল্লিক) is an Indian Bengali Film Actress who appears in Bengali and Odia films. Koel Mallick Established herself as a one of the popular &amp; Highest-Paid Bengali Actress.  Koel debut in Bengali Movie by  Nater guru in 2003. Nater Guru was a \"runaway success\" at the box office and Koel become heartthrob of Bengali audience immediately after this film got released.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel\'s realname is Rukmini. She was born on 28 April 1982 in Kolkata, West Bengal, India. Hence, her current age is [DateCounter startDate=\"1982-04-28\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years. Koel Mallick\'s Zodiac is Taurus. Her hometown is Kolkata, India. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>165 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Meters</td><td>1.65 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Feet Inches</td><td>5\' 5\"</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>58 Kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds </td><td>128 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Shoe Size</td><td>8 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Dress Size</td><td>4 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Dark Brown</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family Members </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel Mallick is the daughter of famous actor Ranjit Mallick and her mother\'s name is Deepa Mallick. She is from Mallick family which is a very pronounced family of kolkata. Furthermore, Their family is well known for their traditional Durga Puja. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1806,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Koel-Mallick-with-Ranjit-Mallick.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Koel-Mallick-with-Ranjit-Mallick.jpg\" alt=\"Koel Mallick with Ranjit Mallick\" class=\"wp-image-1806\"/></a><figcaption>Koel Mallick with Ranjit Mallick</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Boys, affairs, spouse name </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel Mallick got married with Nispal Singh (Rane) on 1 February 2013. She dated Nispal Singh for seven years before their marriage.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1807,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Koel-Mallick-Marriage-Photo.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Koel-Mallick-Marriage-Photo.jpg\" alt=\"Koel Mallick Marriage Photo\" class=\"wp-image-1807\"/></a><figcaption>Koel Mallick Marriage Photo</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Favourite Things and Hobbies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Favourite Food</td><td>Sandesh, Chicken Fry, Fish, \'Phuchka\' (Pani-Puri)</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actor</td><td>Prosenjit Chatterjee</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actress</td><td>Kajol</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Colour</td><td>Yellow</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Sport</td><td>Cricket</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Restaurant</td><td>Keventers</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Destination</td><td>Hill Stations</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salary and Net Worth</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel Mallick’s immovable property amounting to Rs.15 Crore. Furthermore, her Salary per movie is approximately 30 lakhs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education and School, College</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel has completed her schooling from Modern High School for Girls, Kolkata. Later on completed her BSC (Honors) in Psychology from Gokhale Memorial Girls\' College, Kolkata.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1808,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Koel-Mallick-in-Durgapuja.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Koel-Mallick-in-Durgapuja.jpg\" alt=\"Koel Mallick in Durgapuja\" class=\"wp-image-1808\"/></a><figcaption>Koel Mallick in Durgapuja</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact Address   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>House Address</td><td>Koel Mallick\'s parents address is Kolkata\'s notable Mallick Bari of Bhowanipore.</td></tr><tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>She didn\'t like share her Phone number to publicly.</td></tr><tr><td>Email Id</td><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Awards</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>4th Tele Cine Awards 2004 for the film Nater Guru (2003)</li><li> 2006 Kalakar Awards, for Subhodrishti (2005)</li><li> ZEE Bangla Gourav Samman Award for Best Actress (Bolo Na Tumi Amar, 2010)</li><li> Star Jalsha Award for Best Actress (Dui Prithibi, 2010)</li><li> BFJA Awards 2013 for Best Actress Hemlock Society (2012)</li><li> ZEE Bangla Gourav Samman Award for Best Actress (Hemlock Society, 2012)</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Controversy and Facts about Koel