(441, 1, '2019-06-18 18:58:30', '2019-06-18 18:58:30', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona Sen Sharma(কঙ্কনা সেন শর্মা) is an Indian actress, writer, and director. She is Very popular Bollywood Film Actress. Konkona is famous as one of the most respected actresses in Bollywood with her memorable performances right. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona\'s nickname is Koko. She was born on 3 December 1979 in New Delhi, India. Hence, her current age is [DateCounter startDate=\"1979-12-03\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years. Konkona\'s Zodiac is Sagittarius. Her hometown is Kolkata, India. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>155 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Meters</td><td>1.55 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Feet Inches</td><td>5\' 1\"</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>57 Kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds </td><td>126 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Shoe Size</td><td>8 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Dress Size</td><td>4 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Dark Brown</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family Members </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona Sen\'s father is a science writer and journalist, named Mukul Sharma. Her mother is actress and film director Aparna Sen. She was just 5 years old, when her parents split. Her late grandfather, Chidananda Dasguptawas among the co-founders of the Calcutta Film Society. Her grandmother Supriya Dasgupta is a cousin of legendary modern Bengali poet Late Jibanananda Das. She has a son named Haroon Shorey, who was born on March 15th, 2011 in a South Mumbai hospital.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Boys, affairs, spouse name </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona Sen Sharma started dating actor and co-star Ranvir Shorey in 2007 and got married on 3 September 2010. But the couple ended in diroved in 2015. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Favourite Things</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Favourite Food</td><td>Fish</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actor</td><td>Irrfan Khan</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actress</td><td>Tabu</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Book</td><td>Hooked to This Is How You Lose Her by Junot Diaz. She loves to read  mystery and thrillers English novels and her favorite authors are Sherlock Holmes and Agatha Christie.  </td></tr><tr><td>Hobbies</td><td>Reading</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Konkona Sen Sharma filmography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona Sen Sharma was made her debut Hindi Film Indira in 1983 as a child artist. She made her lead role Debut Bengali Thriller Film Ek Je Aachhe Kanya in 2000. She has acted Many Superhit, hit &amp; Flop Hindi &amp; Bengali Movie.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona Sen Sharma most popular films such as Mr and Mrs. Lyer (2002), Page 3 (2005), Omkara (2006), Life in a Metro (2007) and Bengali Movie Gyonar Baksho in 2014 are some of her hit films. She has received two National Film Awards and four Filmfare Awards. Konkana Sensharma  starred in Zoya Akhtar\'s Luck by Chance, opposite Farhan Akhtar. After release, the film get highly positive reviews from critics, for her performance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Other than cinema, In June 2009, Konkona debut in theatre with Atul Kumar\'s The Blue Mug alongside Rajat Kapoor, Vinay Pathak, Ranvir Shorey and Sheeba Chadha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salary and Net Worth</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona has estimated net worth of almost $5 million. She earns almost Rs.75 Lacs to Rs.1 Crore for every movie she plays.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education and School, College</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona has completed her schooling from Modern High School for Girls, Kolkata and Calcutta International School, Kolkata. Later on completed her B.A. degree in English from St. Stephen\'s College, Delhi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact Address   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>House Address</td><td>Goregaon, Mumbai</td></tr><tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>She didn\'t like share her Phone number to publicly.</td></tr><tr><td>Email Id</td><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/I.Am.Konkona.Sen.Sharma/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/konkonas?lang=en</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/konkona/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Konkona_Sen_Sharma</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Facts about Konkona Sen Sharma</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>There is a controversy that, Konkona married Ranvir Shorey in a hurry due to her pregnancy before it.</li><li>Konkona appear first time in movie as a child artist in 1983s \"Indira.\"</li><li>Konkana Sensharma is a feminist and she has always raise her voice for various initiatives for the upliftment of women in society. </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -