(1804, 1, '2019-10-07 14:38:17', '2019-10-07 14:38:17', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel Mallick (কোয়েল মল্লিক) is an Indian Bengali Film Actress who appears in Bengali and Odia films. Koel Mallick Established herself as a one of the popular &amp; Highest-Paid Bengali Actress.  Koel debut in Bengali Movie by  Nater guru in 2003. Nater Guru was a \"runaway success\" at the box office and Koel become heartthrob of Bengali audience immediately after this film got released.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel\'s realname is Rukmini. She was born on 28 April 1982 in Kolkata, West Bengal, India. Hence, her current age is [DateCounter startDate=\"1982-04-28\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years. Koel Mallick\'s Zodiac is Taurus. Her hometown is Kolkata, India. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>165 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Meters</td><td>1.65 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Feet Inches</td><td>5\' 5\"</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>58 Kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds </td><td>128 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Shoe Size</td><td>8 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Dress Size</td><td>4 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Dark Brown</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family Members </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Koel Mallick is the daughter of famous actor Ranjit Mallick and her mother\'s name is Deepa Mallick. She is from Mallick family which is a very pronounced family of kolkata. Their family is well known for their traditional Durga Puja. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Boys, affairs, spouse name </