(1814, 1, '2019-10-08 16:40:20', '2019-10-08 16:40:20', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona Sen Sharma(কঙ্কনা সেন শর্মা) is an Indian actress, writer, and director. She is Very popular Bollywood Film Actress. Konkona is famous as one of the most respected actresses in Bollywood with her memorable performances right. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona\'s nickname is Koko. She was born on 3 December 1979 in New Delhi, India. Hence, her current age is [DateCounter startDate=\"1979-12-03\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years. Konkona\'s Zodiac is Sagittarius. Her hometown is Kolkata, India. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>155 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Meters</td><td>1.55 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Feet Inches</td><td>5\' 1\"</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>57 Kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds </td><td>126 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Shoe Size</td><td>8 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Dress Size</td><td>4 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Dark Brown</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family Members </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Konkona Sen\'s father is a science writer and journalist, named Mukul Sharma. Her mother is actress and film director Aparna Sen. She was just 5 years old, when her parents split. Her late grandfather, Chidananda Dasguptawas among the co-founders of the Calcutta Film Society. Her grandmother Supriya Dasgupta is a cousin of legendary modern Bengali poet Late Jibanananda Das. She has a son named Haroon Shorey, who was born on March 15th, 2011 in a South Mumbai hospital.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->