s Kala Niketan is now a popular and remarkable dance institution of Kolkata.</li><li> She is an active supporter of the People for Animals cause.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indrani_Dutta</td></tr><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/indraniduttakalaniketan/</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Indrani Dutta Photos<br></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[1816,1817,1818],\"linkTo\":\"media\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/indrani-dutta-1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/indrani-dutta-1.jpg\" alt=\"Indrani Dutta HD Photo\" data-id=\"1816\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/indrani-dutta/indrani-dutta-1/#main\" class=\"wp-image-1816\"/></a><figcaption>Indrani Dutta HD Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/indrani-dutta-2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/indrani-dutta-2.jpg\" alt=\"Indrani Dutta Cute Photo\" data-id=\"1817\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/indrani-dutta/indrani-dutta-2-2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-1817\"/></a><figcaption>Indrani Dutta Cute Photo</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/indrani-dutta-3.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/indrani-dutta-3.jpg\" alt=\"Indrani Dutta HD Photo\" data-id=\"1818\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/indrani-dutta/indrani-dutta-3/#main\" class=\"wp-image-1818\"/></a><figcaption>Indra