(1825, 1, '2019-10-08 20:13:51', '2019-10-08 20:13:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Sharma is an Indian Film Actress, Model and Film Producer. She is a very popular Bollywood Film Actress. she is currently one of the leading &amp; commercial successful and one of the Highest-paid Actress of Bollywood. Anushka Sharma has received Several accolades including one Filmfare Award from Seven Nomination. She was made her debut with Shahrukh Khan blockbuster Hit film Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi (2008), which won her Filmfare Best Actress Award. She had her biggest commercial successes with the roles of a television reporter in the religious satire PK (2014) and a wrestler in the sports drama Sultan (2016), both of which rank among the highest-grossing Indian films.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":606,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma Photoshoot\" class=\"wp-image-606\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma Photoshoot</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Sharma\'s nickname is Anu and Nushie. She was born on <strong>1 May 1988</strong> in Ayodhya, Uttar Pradesh, India. Hence, her current age is <strong>[DateCounter startDate=\"1988-05-01\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years</strong>. Anushka\'s Zodiac is Taurus. She basically belongs to Ayodhya, Uttar Pradesh but she grew up in Bengaluru and now she is settled in Mumbai.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><t