wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education and School, College</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anushka Sharma was educated at the Army School, Bengaluru. She was a topper in school. She had received a degree in arts from Mount Carmel College in Bangalore. Anushka completed her Master Degree Program in Economics through correspondence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact Address   </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>House Address</td><td>Badrinath Towers, 20th Floor, Seven Bungalows, Andheri, Mumbai. 3BHK flat at Panch Vatika apartments in Yari Road. </td></tr><tr><td>Phone Number</td><td>She didn\'t like share her Phone number to publicly.</td></tr><tr><td>Email Id</td><td>N/A</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Social Media</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Facebook</td><td>https://www.facebook.com/AnushkaSharmaOfficial/</td></tr><tr><td>Twitter</td><td>https://twitter.com/AnushkaSharma</td></tr><tr><td>Instagram</td><td>https://www.instagram.com/anushkasharma/?hl=en</td></tr><tr><td>Wikipedia</td><td>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anushka_Sharma</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Facts about Anushka Sharma</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Anushka started her modeling career at the Lakme Fashion Week as a model for Wendell Rodricks\'s Les Vamps Show</li><li>Her first ramp walk was at the age of 15.</li><li>She late riser and like to have egg and a glass of fresh juice in breakfast</li><li>Anushka works out 4 times a week and has personal trainer.</li><li>Anushka is a beer drinker.</li><li>While paying her homage to Late Dr APJ Abdul Kalam on twitter, she misspelled his name as \"ABJ Kalam Azad\". After it, she was criticized on twitter and she deleted that tweet and posted another one, which was again wrong as she wrote \"APJ Kalam Azad\". At the third attempt, she finally tweeted it correctly i.e. \"Dr. APJ Abdul Kalam\".</li><li>There was a rift in her relationship with Virat Kohli for a while in the early 2016. If reports are to be believed then the reason behind it was that Virat invested a good amount of money in Anushka\'s film Bombay Velvet, which unfortunately failed at the box office. And, when Virat asked about the money loss to Anushka, she felt upset. Virat even unfollowed her on Twitter and Instagram, but after few months they got back together.</li><li>Apart from acting, Sharma supports a number of charities and causes. She walked the ramp to support Shabana Azmi’s Mijwan Welfare Society, an NGO that helps empower women.</li><li>She supports various charities and causes, including gender equality and animal rights, and is the co-founder of the production company Clean Slate Films. </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Anushka Sharma Photos</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[608,622,624,625,626,627,628],\"linkTo\":\"media\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"aligncenter\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma2.jpg\" alt=\"Anushka Sharma HD Wallpaper\" data-id=\"608\" data-link=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/2019/06/13/anushka-sharma/anushka_sharma2/#main\" class=\"wp-image-608\"/></a><figcaption>Anushka Sharma HD Wallpaper</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-candid-photoshoot.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Anushka_Sharma-candid-photoshoot.