(1826, 1, '2019-10-08 20:22:22', '2019-10-08 20:22:22', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nusrat Jahan (নুসরত জাহান) is an Indian Bengali film actress and also worked as a model. She is one of the most beautiful and popular Bengali movie. She also joined in politics in 2019 and she is the Member of Lok Sabha from Basirhat Constituency from Trinamool Congress.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":464,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-Jahan-bridal-look.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-Jahan-bridal-look.jpg\" alt=\"Nusrat Jahan in bridal look\" class=\"wp-image-464\"/></a><figcaption>Nusrat Jahan in bridal look</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Biography &amp; Wiki</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nusrat Jahan\'s nickname is Nusrat. She was born on 8th January 1990 in Kolkata, India. Hence, her current <strong>age</strong> is <strong>[DateCounter startDate=\"1990-01-08\" endDate=\"now\" format=\"Years\"] years</strong>. Nusrat Zodiac is Capricorn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Height, Weight &amp; Body Measurements</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Height in Centimeters</td><td>170 cm</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Meters</td><td>1.70 m</td></tr><tr><td>Height in Feet Inches</td><td>5\' 7\"</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Kilograms</td><td>56 Kg</td></tr><tr><td>Weight in Pounds </td><td>127 lbs</td></tr><tr><td>Shoe Size</td><td>8 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Dress Size</td><td>4 (US)</td></tr><tr><td>Hair Color</td><td>Black</td></tr><tr><td>Eye Color</td><td>Dark Brown</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Family Members</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nusrat Jahan is a very gorgeous actress belongs to a Bengali Muslim family. She has two sisters named Nuzhat Jahan and Pooja Prassad. Her father and mother names are not available. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":466,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-Jahan-with-dad.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-Jahan-with-dad.jpg\" alt=\"Nusrat-Jahan with her dad\" class=\"wp-image-466\"/></a><figcaption>Nusrat-Jahan with her dad</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Boys, affairs, spouse name </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First of all, She was in a serious relationship with Kader Khan and they broke up after Kader got arrested for a serious criminal case. After that there was a rumour that she was in a relationship with a businessman from Jamshedpur called Victor Ghosh. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":468,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-Jahan-Nikhil-Jain.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-Jahan-Nikhil-Jain.jpg\" alt=\"Nusrat Jahan with Nikhil Jain\" class=\"wp-image-468\"/></a><figcaption>Nusrat Jahan with Nikhil Jain</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nusrat Jahan got married with <strong>Nikhil Jain</strong> in Turkey on 19th June 2019. Nikhil is the director of a leading trader of clothes from Kolkata. Consequently, he completed his initial study from Kolkata. According to media Nusrat and Nikhil met on the advertisement set of this company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Favourite Things</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<table class=\"wp-block-table\"><tbody><tr><td>Best Friend</td><td>Mimi Chakraborty</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Food</td><td>Mutton, Mishti Doi, Pasta</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actor</td><td>Shahrukh Khan</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Actress</td><td>Preity Zinta</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Colours</td><td>Pink, Yellow, Black</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Sport</td><td>Cricket</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Cricketer</td><td>Sourav Ganguly</td></tr><tr><td>Favourite Destination</td><td>Bavaria, Germany  </td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Nusrat Jahan filmography</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First of all, Nusrat has also won the title of Fair One Miss Kolkata in 2010. Her first screen debut was in Raj Chakraborty\'s <strong>Shotru</strong>. After that, she appeared as an movie actress in the film Khoka 420, under the banner Eskay Movies. Apart from this movie, the other notable movies where she worked an an actress are Khiladi with Ankush Hazra, Sondhe Namar Agey with Rahul Bose and Power with Jeet under the banner of Shree Venkatesh Films. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":469,\"align\":\"center\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-with-Mimi.jpg\"><img src=\"http://localhost/bollywikia/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Nusrat-with-Mimi.jpg\" alt=\"Nusrat with Mimi Chakraborty\" class=\"wp-image-469\"/></a><figcaption>Nusrat with her bestie Mimi Chakraborty</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Politics</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>West Bengal Chief Minister and president of Trinamool Congress party Mamata Banerjee announced Nusrat as a candidate for Lok Sabha election 2019. Finally, Nusrat won